    • Christo Godfy
      5.0 out of 5 stars Best Android Tab
      Reviewed in India on 21 October 2024
      Size: Silver | WiFi + 5G | 12GB + 256GB
      I like Samsung S10 Ultra Tab a lot because of these reasons

      1. The display - The 14.6-inch display offers great multimedia experience, I like to watch a lot of content for learning, take notes and so on. And l am so obsessed with these Amoled experience that I feel boring to use an IPS or LCD display, everyone likes Amoled because of the vibrant color, brightness and contrast level it can offer and Samsung displays are best regarding that. I have a good gaming lap that i bought last year costed a lakh , it has powerful processor, good typing experience, great performance always but
      even after that it offers a lot, I feel bored to use it to learn watch a video becauses it's an IPS WUXGA 165Hz display with high refresh rate, so often I use my Samsung phone which has an amoled FHD display, because the display does matter a lot, Because whatever catches our attention in and itself has the potential to change the way we do things even learning often I fall love learning a course online watching the lectures even if some are boring because of the amoled display quality I feel like watching it.

      2. Material Quality -- I got my first phone in 2020 and it was a midrange phone has a polycarbonate back panel and plastic side frame so even if it had a good powerful processor at that time with some good features at that price, the in hand experience made it boring for me.

      Touch and Feel truly changes the experience to the next level, my phone has aluminum frame, and it feels sturdy and strong with a good touch and feel so I can imagine how well this tablet would be it is really an experience to use it for learning . It makes a huge difference

      3. S Pen - As humans, we all have one Great distinct ability - Our Imagination, If we use our imagination, it creates an open road to endless opportunities because we can work on it later as we can write it down in the tablet, as it comes with S Pen , we can draw, take notes, and even add reference from the web and later note it in our notebook also, This is a big benefit

      4. Expanded storage -- This tab has offers a SD card slot that a great benefit nowadays (ultra offering up to 1TB and s10+ up to 512 GB)

      5. Battery - the tab is thin and it comes with 11,200 mah battery so it will give a good battery life

      6. Front and Back Ultra wide camera - Really good to have that because while video calling relatives and friends the ultra wide camera gives a wide view. Even for Online meetings it is a nice to have feature

      7. Samsung Dex --> it is one feature that makes it really good because you can use two screens at one time connecting it with a monitor or lap screen , Can use most apps in lap screen with the lap keyboard and simultaneously watch something and type it in notes , OneNote. I like that feature a lot, in this tab it gives a dual screen experience as (for me) watch a lecture/video and take notes in parallel because of that great feature.
